{"tid":1162902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【13省淪陷】「糧食殺手」草地貪夜蛾 7月隨風勢殺到東北","createTime":"2019-05-20T06:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T18:16:45.000Z","uid":125193,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"49e66be97303f7f1649e107877ee3f23ffc0586e","tid":1162902,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T06:33:12.000Z","msg":"自今年1月入侵雲南後，草地貪夜蛾已迅速蔓延至13省。專家預計，草地貪夜蛾將隨着季候風，向內地中部和北部前進，或將於6月份進入黃淮的粟米主產區，在7月份到達東北粟米主產區。農業農村部正在加強監測防治蟲害。<br />\n<br />\n「草地貪夜蛾」被聯合國糧農組織預警的重大害蟲，具有超強的飛行能力，2017年已被國際農化中心（Centre for Agriculture and Biosciences International, CABI）列入世界十大植物害蟲黑名單的第8位。<br />\n<br />\n今年以來，草地貪夜蛾已經肆虐中國南方多地，根據全國農業技術推廣服務中心5月14日的最新數據，雲南、廣西、貴州、廣東、湖南、海南、福建、浙江、湖北、四川、江西、重慶、河南等相繼省份，均發現草地貪夜蛾幼蟲，草地貪夜蛾蔓延更有加快趨勢。"},{"pid":"467996f46813102a5825f14e06cf4191565a580a","tid":1162902,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T06:33:21.000Z","msg":"【13省淪陷】「糧食殺手」草地貪夜蛾 7月隨風勢殺到東北<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190519&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59618395\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190519%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59618395&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ1x3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=3d8bd0e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190519%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59618395&h=6e0a2f64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190519&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59618395</a>"},{"pid":"500d591c9421c32ea4a9e1198b09f8aaeb51f686","tid":1162902,"uid":9291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T06:34:48.000Z","msg":"多難興邦"},{"pid":"33227c501f1397c8ac99fa45e8b686a8fe99fcc1","tid":1162902,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T06:35:56.000Z","msg":"香港有冇?"},{"pid":"115302de43c9a83f81368880df2d1ea83309d90d","tid":1162902,"uid":49004,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"quote":{"pid":"33227c501f1397